ActCanada Transportation Act
PrecisAppointment of MARK A. M. GAUTHIER of Gatineau, Quebec, to be the Administrator of the Fund for Railway Accidents Involving Designated Goods,on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year, or until such time as a new administrator is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective April 3, 2023.
